<bibRefCitation box="[755,1012,1007,1032]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" refId="ref67574" refString="Takaoka, H. &amp; Sigit, S. H. (1992) A new blackfly species of Simulium (Gomphostilbia) from Java, Indonesia (Diptera: Simuliidae). Japanese Journal of Tropical Medicine and Hygiene, 20, 135 - 142. https: // doi. org / 10.2149 / tmh 1973.20.135" type="journal article">Takaoka &amp; Sigit, 1992</bibRefCitation>
